	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "This class and its enumerated subclasses represent standardized types of PoE DC electricity.\n\n: DC-PoE Enumerations\n\n| Enumeration |\n|:-----------|\n| `PoE-802.3af-1` |\n| `PoE-802.3at-2` |\n| `PoE-802.3bt-3` |\n| `PoE-802.3bt-4` |" ;
