<http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#Relation> a <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#Class> , <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#Class> , <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#Concept> , <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#NodeShape> ;
	<http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#property> _:a2bb674e9110e1f20ae0fdff17b7b808 ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A `Relation` associates the subject and the object in an RDF triple, the *predicate* portion of a *(subject, predicate, object)* triple." ;
