	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The relation `hasFreezingPoint` is used to associate a freezing point with a glycol solution, but could be used with other `Substance-Medium`s as appropriate." ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has freezing point" .
