	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A piece of `Equipment` that uses fuel or electricity to heat water or other fluids and supply steam or hot water for heating, humidification, or other applications." ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Boiler" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#Equipment> .
