	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The domain that represents equipment that illuminate and manage the distribution of light within or outside of a building. Example `Domain-Lighting` equipment include `Luminaire`, `LightSensor`, and `WindowShade`." ;
