<http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#Medium-Constituent> a <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#Medium-Constituent> , <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#Class> , <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#NodeShape> ;
	<http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#property> _:b3a3e3e6d395bab30be58c6481fa1dca ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "\nThis class and its enumerated subclasses represent substances that may be combined to form a `Medium-Mix`. Constituents are distinguished from `Medium-Mix` and its subclasses in that constituents cannot use the `composedOf` relation to reference a concentration of other constituents.\n\n: Medium-Constituent Enumerations\n\n| Enumeration |\n|:-----------|\n| `Constituent-Ar` |\n| `Constituent-CH4` |\n| `Constituent-CO` |\n| `Constituent-CO2` |\n| `Constituent-Electricity` (see {s223:Constituent-Electricity}) |\n| `Constituent-EM` (see {s223:Constituent-EM}) |\n| `Constituent-Glycol` |\n| `Constituent-H2O` |\n| `Constituent-H2S` |\n| `Constituent-N2` |\n| `Constituent-NH3` |\n| `Constituent-NOX` (see {s223:Constituent-NOX}) |\n| `Constituent-O2` |\n| `Constituent-O3` |\n| `Constituent-Oil` |\n| `Constituent-Radon` |\n| `Constituent-Refrigerant` (see {s223:Constituent-Refrigerant}) |\n| `Constituent-SO2` |\n| `Constituent-VolatileOrganicCompounds` |\n" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Constituent" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#Substance-Medium> .
<http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#Function> a <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#Class> , <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#NodeShape> ;
	<http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#property> _:afc4a9823718f77554779241b02f8cbe , _:e2cec01d2448b6f0b3d711903a56d103 ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A `Function` is used to model transfer and/or transformation of information (i.e., `Property`). It has relations to input Properties and output Properties. The actual algorithms that perform the transformations are described in CDL and are out of scope of the 223 standard." ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Function" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#Concept> .
