	<http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#severity> <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#Warning> ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A `Radiator` shall have at least one inlet using the medium Electricity or inlet and outlet of Water." ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Radiator inlet shape" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#message> "s223: A `Radiator` shall have at least one inlet using the medium Electricity or inlet and outlet of Water." .
