	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A `Relation` that associates a piece of `Equipment` with the `ActuatableProperty` that it responds to. If the `Equipment`\nis an `Actuator` (a subclass of `Equipment`), `actuatedByProperty` is a required relation. An `Actuator` may also identify another piece of\n`Equipment` being actuated (see {s223:actuates})." ;
