	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "This class and its enumerated subclasses represent common forms of electrical energy, including AC, DC, and electrical communication signals.\n\n: Constituent-Electricity Enumerations\n\n| Enumeration |\n|:-----------|\n| `Electricity-AC` (see {s223:Electricity-AC}) |\n| `Electricity-DC` (see {s223:Electricity-DC}) |\n| `Electricity-Earth` |\n| `Electricity-Neutral` |\n| `Electricity-Signal` (see {s223:Electricity-Signal}) |" ;
