	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A piece of `Equipment` that collects human waste (i.e., urine and/or feces, and sometimes toilet paper) in a chamber containing water,\nand contains an integral manual or automatic actuator that triggers the release of an additional volume of water that flushes everything from the chamber into\na drainage system that typically carries the mixture to a sewer system or septic tank." ;
