	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A piece of equipment that automatically opens an electric circuit automatically at a predetermined overcurrent, so as to prevent damage to the circuit, the equipment connected to the circuit, and the building containing the circuit." ;
