	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The domain that represents equipment that control and monitor physical access to spaces within or outside of a building. Example `Domain-PhysicalSecurity` equipment include cameras, keycard sensors, and biometric scanners." ;
