	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "This class and its enumerated subclasses represent building systems and services (e.g., HVAC, Lighting, and Plumbing).\n\n: EnumerationKind-Domain Enumerations\n\n| Enumeration |\n|:-----------|\n| `Domain-ConveyanceSystems` |\n| `Domain-Electrical` |\n| `Domain-FireProtection` |\n| `Domain-HVAC` |\n| `Domain-Lighting` |\n| `Domain-Networking` |\n| `Domain-Occupancy` |\n| `Domain-PhysicalSecurity` |\n| `Domain-Plumbing` |\n| `Domain-Refrigeration` |" ;
