	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A piece of `Equipment` that can be programmed to automatically carry out sequences of arithmetic or logical operations (computation).\nModern digital electronic computers can perform generic sets of operations known as programs. These programs enable computers to perform a\nwide range of tasks." ;
