	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "If the property identified is of datatype array, this optional property of type Unsigned shall indicate the array index of\nthe element of the `Property` referenced by the ReadProperty service or the Read Access Specification of the ReadPropertyMultiple service. If the bacnet:property-array-index is omitted, this shall mean that the entire\narray shall be referenced.  See ASHRAE 135-2024 Clause 15.5.1.1.3 and Clause 15.7.1.1.1." ;
