_:ba0fca9a76102a07256bff1fcc95a297 <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#class> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/QuantityValue> ;
	<http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#path> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/quantityValue> ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A `QuantifiableProperty` shall be associated with zero or more `qudt:QuantityValue`s using the relation `qudt:quantityValue`. This allows to express multiple equivalent combinations of a `Unit` and value. However, typically a `QuantifiableProperty` is associated with a static decimal value using `hasValue`, along with a single `Unit` and `QuantityKind`." ;
	<http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#message> "s223: A `QuantifiableProperty` shall be associated with zero or more `qudt:QuantityValue`s using the relation `qudt:quantityValue`. This allows to express multiple equivalent combinations of a `Unit` and value. However, typically a `QuantifiableProperty` is associated with a static decimal value using `hasValue`, along with a single `Unit` and `QuantityKind`." .
