	a <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#SPARQLConstraint> ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "If an incoming relation `composedOf` exists, then the `Property` must have a declared substance using the relation `ofConstituent`." ;
